         <abstract id="aspace_079dcde471b4006d04ffc177aa8af651">The collection comprises digital video files made from videotapes documenting the Cherry Bowl Volleyball Tournament, an annual charity beach volleyball tournament, begun in 1984, pitting the Cherry Grove Grovettes against various emergency services and police departments from the Long Island and New York City area.</abstract>
